sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant DB as Postgres
    participant S3 as MinIO/S3
    participant Embed as Embedding<br/>(local or Bedrock)

    User->>FE: choose file
    FE->>API: POST /api/documents (multipart)
    API->>DB: INSERT documents (status=pending)
    API->>S3: put_object(storage_key, bytes)
    API->>DB: UPDATE documents SET status=processing

    API->>API: parse → list[ParsedPage]
    API->>API: chunk → list[Chunk] (800 tokens, 100 overlap)

    API->>Embed: embed_batch(texts)
    Embed-->>API: list[1024-dim vectors]

    API->>DB: bulk INSERT chunks (text, page, embedding)
    API->>DB: UPDATE documents SET status=indexed,<br/>chunk_count=N, indexed_at=NOW()
    API-->>FE: 201 Created (Document JSON)
    FE-->>User: "indexed · N chunks"
